<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->A former Demon Slayer Corps member has appeared at your settlement. They offer to escort up to three of your colonists to Mount Sagiri for the Final Selection - a seven-day survival trial where participants fight captured demons in a wisteria-enclosed mountain.\n\nOnly those who survive all seven nights and claim their ore at dawn will join the Demon Slayer Corps. Your colonists may develop the ability to learn breathing techniques... if they can endure.\n\nThe retired slayer's scarred face speaks volumes: "Many climb Mount Sagiri. Most feed the demons. The worthy few descend forever changed."\n\nSurvival depends on combat skills, physical resilience, and sheer determination. Skilled fighters and tough individuals have better odds, while the frail face greater peril.\n\nWARNING: Colonists with demon blood cannot participate - the wisteria barriers would kill them instantly.</li>
  -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
  <li>questDescription->一名前鬼殺隊士出現在你的定居點。他提出可以將你的三名殖民者，護送到狹霧山參加最終選拔。那是一場為期七天的生存試煉，參加者需在紫藤花環繞的山中，與被監禁的鬼交戰。\n\n只有成功活過七夜，並在明晨挑選自己玉鋼的人，才能加入鬼殺隊。你的殖民者可能從中得到學習呼吸法的能力……前提是他們能忍受下來。\n\n退休隊士佈滿傷痕的臉說明了一切:「登上狹霧山，多數成鬼餐。少有貴刀人，轉命步返程。」\n\n生存取決於格鬥技能、身體韌性和堅強的意志。敏捷的戰士與意志堅定者更有勝算，而體弱者會面臨更大的危險。\n\n警告: 擁有鬼之血的殖民者不得參加，因為紫藤花園林會立即將其殺害。</li>
  </AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
