  <!-- EN: Demon Slayer Corps Guide Arrived -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>鬼殺隊引路人已抵達</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: A veteran of the Demon Slayer Corps has arrived to escort your colonists to Mount Sagiri. Their haori bears the Corps' symbol, and their eyes hold the weight of countless battles.\n\n"Seven nights among demons. Send one to three candidates. Those who survive join our ranks. Those who fall become demon feast."\n\nChoose wisely - combat skills and physical toughness improve survival odds, while frailty makes the trial far more perilous.\n\nIMPORTANT: Colonists with demon blood CANNOT participate. The wisteria barriers surrounding Mount Sagiri are lethal to demons. -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>一位資深鬼殺隊士前來接送你的殖民者前往狹霧山。他的羽織印有鬼殺隊的標誌，眼神背負了無數戰鬥帶來的沉重。\n\n「七晚與鬼為伍，選出一到三名應試者吧。生者為隊士，敗者為鬼飧。」\n\n謹慎選擇⸺格鬥技能和體質能提高生存率，而體弱者會在試煉面臨更大的危機。\n\n重要提醒: 擁有鬼之血的殖民者不得參加，因為狹霧山周圍的紫藤花林對鬼是致命的。</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ShuttleDelay.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Final Selection Results -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>最終選拔結果</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The transport has returned from Mount Sagiri. The survival rolls have been made, and fates have been decided... -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>運輸艙已從狹霧山返回。已完成生存判定，而他們的命運也塵埃落定……</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Final Selection Rewards -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterLabel.slateRef>最終選拔獎勵</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterLabel.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Rewards from the Final Selection have arrived via transport pod. -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterText.slateRef>最終選拔的獎勵已經由運輸艙送達。</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsReturned.node.nodes.DropPods.customLetterText.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Final Selection - Total Failure -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>最終選拔 ⸺ 全軍覆沒</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.label.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: No one has returned from Mount Sagiri. The demons have claimed all who entered. Their sacrifice will not be forgotten, but the Corps gains no new members this day. -->
  <AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>沒有人從狹霧山回來。鬼抓走了所有進入山中的參加者。雖然他們的犧牲永遠不會被忘記，但鬼殺隊一個新成員都沒有增加。</AnimeArsenal_MountSagiriFinalSelection.root.nodes.ColonistsDied.node.nodes.Letter.text.slateRef>
  
